      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition, still smelling like new. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine and transmission operate with the precision of a brand-new car, and all service records are up to date. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. You can expect a smooth, worry-free experience with absolutely no repairs or detailing required.",
