      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a reliable ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures with you! It runs beautifully and looks great, too. I\u2019m happy to answer any questions you have or hop on a quick call\u2014I want to make sure it's the perfect fit for you!",
