    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders with the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) delivering sharp transitional throttle response. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts precisely, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. It features a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential and a refreshed cooling system including a high-flow water pump. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the VANOS system has been serviced and the rod bearings have been addressed, ensuring this chassis is ready for high-lateral-G maneuvers.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
