    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and performance. The exterior features a deep, glossy finish with only minor road-pebble marks on the front bumper, typical of a well-loved daily driver. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned, showing only slight softening on the driver's side bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system and heated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust\u2014I have adhered strictly to the manufacturer's maintenance schedule, including a recent full fluid flush and brake inspection. The tires have plenty of life left, and the engine runs smoothly without any leaks or noises. It\u2019s a turn-key car ready for its next owner to enjoy the road with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
